                    <value>&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Hey {{{Recipient.FirstName}}},&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Now that you&amp;rsquo;ve created your 10X Patient Portal account, have you filled out your&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;consent&lt;/strong&gt; forms?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Remember, &lt;strong&gt;we can&amp;rsquo;t take the next step in your wellness journey until those are complete.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;So- how do you fill out your forms?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Step 1:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://portal.10xhealthsystem.com&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Click here to login to your 10X Patient Portal account.&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Step 2: &lt;/b&gt;At the very top of the screen, you&amp;rsquo;ll see a notification banner with a red button. Click that button.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Step 3:&lt;/b&gt; Complete the information fields as necessary. Click &amp;lsquo;Save &amp;amp; Continue&amp;rsquo;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Step 4:&lt;/b&gt; Return to your portal homepage. Click the arrow on the upper righthand side of your screen to confirm documents have been submitted.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Note:&lt;/b&gt; If there&amp;rsquo;s more than one form for you to complete, it will automatically bring up the next form once you Save &amp;amp; Continue. Please fill out all forms until a success window appears.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Again, we can&amp;#39;t move forward without signed consent forms.&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://portal.10xhealthsystem.com&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Click here to log in and complete your forms.&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Once your forms are done, you&amp;#39;re one step closer to feeling the way you deserve.&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;To your wellness,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
